Prompt 1 (Idea Generation)
I am building a developer conference website called DevConf 2026.
Suggest a modern Newsletter Signup section that fits the website. The section should encourage developers to subscribe for speaker announcements, workshop updates, ticket discounts, and developer resources. Keep the design simple, modern, and professional.

Prompt 2 (Code Generation)
Create a responsive Newsletter Signup section for my DevConf 2026 website using HTML5 and CSS3 only.
The section should have:
 A two-column layout
 A heading and short description
A list of benefits
An email input field
 A "Subscribe Now" button
 A small message: "No spam. Unsubscribe anytime."
Use a modern dark theme with blue accents, rounded corners, smooth hover effects, and Flexbox. Write clean, semantic HTML and organized CSS.